title: #92Noon Nordo in for PA: Burnsy/Zimmer Presser/Leber/Patterson/Korzenowski
description: Eric Nordiquist is in for PA today and there is much to discuss. Celebrating Signing Day with Ryan Burns from Gopher Illustrated. Mike Zimmer's Presser from TCO. Ben Leber joins in studio to talk his time with the Chargers and the Border Battle. X's & O's with Defensive Lineman coach, Andre Patterson & PA. And the FAN's Scott Korzenowski joins in studio to talk Vikings, Wolves, & Gophers.
